### Add Items to Quote
# Adds new products to an existing quote
# Products must NOT already exist in the quote (use update endpoint to change quantity)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/default/V1/shops/{{shopId}}/integration/quote/{{quoteMaskId}}/items/add
Authorization: Bearer {{sharedSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "sku": "24-WB05",
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "product_id": 5,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

